### The Blocker Mod - Known Issues - Version 0.8 - Beta

1. Support for vanilla Mastery of Nature and Environmentalist is limited to vanilla features until I decide how to handle those mechanics in the mod.

2. The Imperial Fiefdom origin hasn't been extensively tested yet as I haven't had enough games with Overlord to get a feel for its balance yet.

3. Some scripted systems may still spawn planets without features. If your favourite unique planet is now a featureless hellscape, please leave a bug report (ideally with the initializer name if you know it). To fix any planet like this in-game, select the planet, open the console, and type the following: effect reroll_deposits = yes
